05/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-series-of-mistakes-led-to-killing-of-world-central-kitchen-workers-in-gaza/0000018e-acb9-d906-a5cf-aebd1f560000</guid></item><item><title>“耶路撒冷有很多无法解释的事情”：游览一座鬼城</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-05/ty-article-magazine/.premium/jerusalem-has-a-lot-of-unexplainable-things-taking-a-tour-around-a-city-of-ghosts/0000018e-aaa4-dc42-a3de-aab6ad0a0000</link><description>导游伊塔马尔·法尔希（Itamar Farhi）多年来一直在进行“耶路撒冷的恐惧与厌恶”之旅，展示了这座城市所有最残酷的地点。在下个星期五 13 号之前，《国土报》将进行可怕的旅程</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Apr 2024 08:12:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-05/ty-article-magazine/.premium/jerusalem-has-a-lot-of-unexplainable-things-taking-a-tour-around-a-city-of-ghosts/0000018e-aaa4-dc42-a3de-aab6ad0a0000</guid></item><item><title>外国外交官表示，以色列与哈马斯的谈判可能持续数周，但协议并不是内塔尼亚胡的首要任务</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-05/ty-article/.premium/foreign-diplomat-says-israel-hamas-talks-could-last-weeks-deal-isnt-netanyahus-priority/0000018e-aa9d-d906-a5cf-aa9d03600000</link><description>这位特使表示，他可以看出哈马斯将拒绝最新的停火提议，因为它与之前的提议没有太大不同</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Apr 2024 03:02:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-05/ty-article/.premium/foreign-diplomat-says-israel-hamas-talks-could-last-weeks-deal-isnt-netanyahus-priority/0000018e-aa9d-d906-a5cf-aa9d03600000</guid></item><item><title>六个月后，以色列-加沙战争的目标几乎没有实现</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-05/ty-article/.premium/after-six-months-few-of-the-israel-gaza-wars-goals-have-been-achieved/0000018e-aa80-d029-a78f-faa25a8a0000</link><description>尽管对加沙发动地面入侵有一定的逻辑性，但必须承认失败：期望太高，与美国的紧张局势加剧，人质仍在加沙</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Apr 2024 03:01:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-05/ty-article/.premium/after-six-months-few-of-the-israel-gaza-wars-goals-have-been-achieved/0000018e-aa80-d029-a78f-faa25a8a0000</guid></item><item><title>