-04-04/ty-article/.premium/biden-to-netanyahu-u-s-gaza-policy-to-be-based-on-israel-curbing-civilian-harm/0000018e-aa42-ddd5-a7ef-afc27eb00000</link><description>自以色列在加沙发动袭击导致七名世界中央厨房援助人员死亡以来，拜登在第一次通话中强调，以色列必须采取具体措施保护加沙平民和援助人员，否则美国对以色列在加沙战争中的支持可能会发生变化</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 18:29:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-04/ty-article/.premium/biden-to-netanyahu-u-s-gaza-policy-to-be-based-on-israel-curbing-civilian-harm/0000018e-aa42-ddd5-a7ef-afc27eb00000</guid></item></channel></rss>